Node.Notes: Uncertain. Assumes apposition to elided [the land of] the Gebalite. 1k5:32 mentions the Gebalites.
The half-tribe of Manasseh in v. 7 is West Manasseh and the half-tribe of Manasseh here is the other half, East Manasseh.
Apparently refers to all the territories mentioned in 13:9-12.
Assumes the Jordan and the territory to ... means: with the Jordan as a border as far as the tip of the Sea of Kinnereth on the east-Jordan side.
